    <section class="site-section container pb-5">
      <div class="glass open-source-box mx-auto p-4 p-md-5">
        <h2 class="h3 text-warning mb-3">Open source</h2>
        <p class="subtle mb-3">
          This <strong>website</strong> is open source. You can report issues, suggest documentation fixes,
