        </p>
        <p class="subtle mb-4">
          The <strong>desktop app source code</strong> is planned to be released later. Until then,
          use the portable ZIP from the download page.
        </p>
        <a href="#" data-signpack-github class="btn btn-warning">Contribute on GitHub</a>
      </div>
